            "title": "Agricultural pests consumed by common bat species in the United States corn belt: The importance of DNA primer choice",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Michael D.",
                    "lastName": "Whitby"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Troy J.",
